  <h1> Tim Bailey Drums </h1>
<div>
<div>
<p class="subheading">I am a professional drummer offering drum kit performance, recording and tuition in Greater Manchester.</p>

<p class="subheading">From my studio in South Manchester I offer the opportunity to learn what YOU want to learn, on the best quality equipment money can buy, for a fair price. Most importantly I offer the opportunity to have fun, learn new skills and relax in a friendly environment!</p>
