<div>
  <h2>Knowledge Gained Though Experience</h2>



<p>Since picking up the sticks at age 6 I have worked in many musical situations including theaters, festivals and studios as well as prestigious live music venues around the UK and Europe. I have extensive experience teaching all ages in '1 on 1' lessons and group sessions of up to 50 people.</p>
